{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ever found yourself captivated by constructing small sculptures with board game pieces while waiting your turn to play? Welcome to this small sandbox game that embraces this very experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in the meditative process of building mesmerizing structures, allowing time to slip away unnoticed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456260/extras/wwmt_about_banner_stack-pieces.png?t=1729004107\" />Move and stack various pieces to construct captivating structures. Arrange and rearrange them to bring your imagination to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456260/extras/wwmt_about_banner_sandbox.png?t=1729004107\" />Enter a realm of boundless creativity with in this sandbox game. In this unrestricted environment, there are no limits or constraints. Build to your heart's content, experiment with different designs, and let your imagination run wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2456260/extras/wwmt_about_banner_relax-and-and-enjoy.png?t=1729004107\" />A stress-free experience with no time limits or puzzles to solve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A world where the only limit is your imagination. Explore endless possibilities and let your artistic flair shine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stack</strong>, <strong>create</strong>, and <strong>enjoy </strong>the blissful process of building extraordinary structures in this captivating small game.</p>","background":"https://sha